OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FThe government announced tougher
OL,7,Fpowers for the consumer watchdog in an
OL,8,Feffort to combat price gouging amid
OL,9,Fthe ongoing conflict in Iran.
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves addressed MPs
OL,12,Fin the Commons on Tuesday, to outline
OL,13,Fthe measures she intends to take to
OL,14,Fprotect households from rising energy
OL,15,Fbills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
