OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FHer announcement follows a Cobra
OL,7,Fmeeting chaired by the prime minister
OL,8,Fon Monday, in which cabinet ministers
OL,9,Fdiscussed the issues of energy supply
OL,10,Fand rising bills as a result of the
OL,11,Fwar in Iran.
OL,13,FConcerns have been raised about both
OL,14,Fthe UK's access to fuel and the effect
OL,15,Fthis is having on energy costs and
OL,16,Fhousehold bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
