FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FConsumers' energy bills are currently
OL,7,Fprotected by the energy price cap
OL,8,Funtil the end of June, meaning energy
OL,9,Fbills will fall in the short-term, as
OL,10,Fthe cap was calculated before the
OL,11,Fconflict began.
OL,13,FConcerns centre on what happens after
OL,14,FJune, when an anticipated higher cap
OL,15,Fis introduced.
OL,17,FAddressing MPs on Tuesday, Reeves
OL,18,Fdescribed the future as "uncertain" as
OL,19,Fshe set out her plans to help those
OL,20,Fmost in need.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
