OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FThe changing situation in the Middle
OL,7,FEast
OL,9,FOn Tuesday, the global markets showed
OL,10,Fsome sign of recovery, with the price
OL,11,Fof oil falling below $100 a barrel.
OL,13,FThis followed the US President Donald
OL,14,FTrump's apparent climb down from his
OL,15,Fprevious threats to target Iran's
OL,16,Fpower infrastructure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
