CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FDespite this apparent cooling of
OL,7,Ftensions, Starmer warned MPs on Monday
OL,8,Fthat it would be wrong to assume this
OL,9,Fconflict may have a swift resolution
OL,10,Fand that the government should prepare
OL,11,Ffor all eventualities.
OL,13,FAddressing MPs, Reeves said the
OL,14,Feconomic challenges from the Iran war
OL,15,Fmay be "significant", and claimed
OL,16,Fcontingency planning was underway for
OL,17,Fenergy bill support "for those who
OL,18,Fneed it most".
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@TO]yD@UOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
