OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FClamp down on price gouging
OL,13,FReeves also announced new powers for
OL,14,Fthe consumer rights watchdog to tackle
OL,15,Fcompanies suspected of exploiting the
OL,16,FMiddle East conflict to increase
OL,17,Fprofits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
