PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FThese will include an "anti-
OL,7,Fprofiteering framework" to detect and
OL,8,Fcrack down on companies exploiting the
OL,9,FMiddle East crisis and help the
OL,10,FCompetition and Markets Authority root
OL,11,Fout price gouging.
OL,13,FThe announcement comes after Starmer
OL,14,Ftold the liaison committee of MPs on
OL,15,FMonday that he was looking at boosting
OL,16,Fthe competition regulator's powers,
OL,17,Fgiving it "further teeth" to deal with
OL,18,Fprofiteering.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@WO]yD@KOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
