CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,F"Later this week I am holding meetings
OL,7,Fwith supermarkets and banks to discuss
OL,8,Fhow they can further support their
OL,9,Fcustomers," the chancellor said.
OL,11,F"Today I can announce that we are
OL,12,Fgoing further to make sure that the
OL,13,Fcompetition and markets authority have
OL,14,Fthe powers they they need that were
OL,15,Fdenied to them by the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment to detect and crack down on
OL,17,Fprice gouging.
OL,19,F"This government will not tolerate any
OL,20,Fcompany exploiting this crisis at
OL,21,Fconsumers' expense," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
