PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FBacking energy security projects
OL,8,FThe chancellor stressed the importance
OL,9,Fof a diverse mix of energy to shield
OL,10,Fthe public from volatile fossil fuel
OL,11,Fmarkets.
OL,13,F"I will not tolerate red tape and
OL,14,Fvested interests holding back our
OL,15,Fenergy security," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
