PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FPointing to large energy projects,
OL,7,Fwhich can often face local objection,
OL,8,FReeves stressed the importance of not
OL,9,Fletting "blockers" get in the way,
OL,10,Fsaying the government will legislate
OL,11,Fto protect these projects with
OL,12,Finsurance policies for large energy
OL,13,Finfrastructure projects being built in
OL,14,Fthe UK.
OL,16,FThese indemnities would allow
OL,17,Fconstruction on large energy projects
OL,18,Fto continue, knowing they were
OL,19,Fsupported should they be legally
OL,20,Fchallenged.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
