OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,F"Energy security is national
OL,7,Fsecurity," Reeves said.
OL,9,FDirect support for consumers
OL,11,FReeves stopped short of announcing
OL,12,Ffull details of support packages the
OL,13,Fgovernment were committing to, but did
OL,14,Foutline the broad strokes of who might
OL,15,Fqualify.
OL,17,FMany will remember the universal
OL,18,Fsupport packages offered by Liz Truss
OL,19,Fwhen energy bills soared on account of
OL,20,FRussia's war in Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
