FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774386358
OL,3,CHow does the government plan to help
OL,4,Cwith your energy bills?
OL,6,FReeves claimed this universal support
OL,7,Fsaw the top 10% of earners receive an
OL,8,Faverage of #1350 of direct energy bill
OL,9,Fsupport, describing this as "a cheque
OL,10,Fwritten then for a bill still being
OL,11,Fpaid today."
OL,13,FTurning away from this approach, the
OL,14,Fchancellor said Labour would deliver
OL,15,F"targeted support for those that need
OL,16,Fit most."
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
